\id 2TI - Etulo
\h 2 iTimoti
\toc1 Afɛ mgbi iPol ongwu fan mbi iTimoti
\toc2 2 iTimoti
\toc3 2iTim
\mt2 Afɛ mgbi iPol // ongwu fan mbi
\mt1 iTimoti
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Afɛ nɛ kyɛ mbi ani iPol, ongye ogbikye iKrestu iYesu mi oweka mgbi Imgbasho. O dɔ ani esɔ gbɛɛ ni ani wa nya inggisɛ angbeka oshishe ongwu o zondu mbi iKrestu iYesu nani.
\p 
\v 2 Ongwani ongwi itukwu-itukwu iTimoti,
\pi1 Elela yi elela odiidi bɛyi iyu ntɔ mbi Imgbasho Otseyi yi iKrestu iYesu Otsɛ mgbi eyi nu ma dzɛ yi abu.
\s1 IPol kwu iTimoti ɛwɛ wo
\p 
\v 3 Ani ta Imgbasho ongwu ani le sunun na angba dafi emi otsikyani tugbe li kyɔ nani, mi itukwu asisa ani li le wɛ abu mi ibɔ mgbi ani otu yi onɔ duu.
\v 4 Ngwi ani wɛ etse mgbi abu nɛ, i mina ani odi abu, ikye ni atsa mbwo ani itukwu.
\v 5 Ani li wɛ oyɛyɛ onuunu otsitsi ndzɛ mbi abu, nteyi dzɛ mbi onikyabu iLoisi bɛyi onabu iYunisi kpaa nani, n di ye saan ta gbɛɛ dzɛ mbi abu kpaa onɛnɛni.
\v 6 Mi itɔdzɛ nɛ n le wɛ abu ikyegbɛɛ umba mgbi Imgbasho ongwi o kye nu abu mi onɔ ngwi ani kye abɔ dɔ abu ikye na, no kiyayi okyidɔ saan.
\v 7 Lubana Imgbasho kye onodzi imio nu eyi ba kpaa, li onodzi mgbi mfye, yi okpitukwu bɛyi onyɛ eweyi.
\p 
\v 8 Nghanɛ ka kwayiwi okyɔ obɛwndɛ mi ikye Otsɛ mgbi eyi ba, naadi ayiwi no ka kwu abu yi ani inggisɛ obawi mgban nɛ ba. Nghaduu kye abɔ bɛ yi ani mi mfye mgbi Imgbasho ni i gyadzɛ mi ikye Esɔ Osuse,
\v 9 ongwu Imgbasho dulu eyi tɔ, di kwu eyi ela gbɛɛ ni eyi dzɛ mi oshishe osaan li ikye unka ngwi eyi kyɔ ba, kpaa li ikye itɔdzɛ bɛyi elela mgban. O kye elela nɛ nu eyi mbi iKrestu iYesu duuse ɛsɛ wa wuta,
\v 10 kpaa onɛnɛ a tson tɔ mi ododa mi obaaba mgbi Ongye onagbɛ eyi iKrestu iYesu ongwu ndzili ikwongye di kye oshishe igyegwu ba bɛyi oshishe nka bwa ba na nyɛ mi esɔ mgban osuse tsotɔ mi osa nani.
\v 11 Di li mi esɔ nɛ ngwi Imgbasho dulu ani oli ongye ogbeesɔ di li inggisɛ ogbikye iYesu di li otsetse aani.
\v 12 Li ikye ungwɔnɛ ngwi ani le gyadzɛ nɛ ngha aani, kpaa ayiwi kwu ani mi ele ba, ikyekyɛ ani ye ongwu ani nun oyɛyɛ nani, n di ye saan ta gbɛɛ o ka yagba ongyo ungwɔ ngwi ani kye dɔn ubɔ ikye egbe nani.
\p 
\v 13 Ungwɔ ngwi abu fwo mbi ani yɔ kyɛdɔ, no li ambɛ mgbi ungwɔ otsootso osuse yi oyɛyɛ onuunu bɛyi okpitukwu mi ifu iKrestu iYesu.
\v 14 Gbɛwɛbyi ungwɔ osuse ongwi a kye wo abu abɔ nani, ni Onodzi Osaan nwodzɛ mbi eyi nɛ ya abu abɔ.
\p 
\v 15 Abu ye dafi ali inggisɛ mi ayɛsɛ Asia duu kyata iyikpa tsɛ ani mani, iFigelu bɛyi iHemogɛnɛ jokpaa kyɔ ngha.
\p 
\v 16 Nghaduu Otsɛ no di udɛ mgbi Onesiforu duu elela, ikyesinɛ o kyile ani itukwu esho onɔ ibyibyi, o di yama kwayiwi ani gbɛɛ ani wodzɛ itse ba.
\v 17 Ngwi o wa kaka iRoma ma, o gbili ani kpatsɛ nghataa o wa tu ani.
\v 18 Abu ye saan dafi mi Efesu ma kpaa, o ya ani abɔ mi ofɛ gwuba mani. N bibɔ gbɛɛ Otsɛ no di Onesiforu elela mi egbe ikwɔ mani.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Nghanɛ, ongwani, Imgbasho no nu abu kwudzɛ kpɔklɔɔ mi elela ndzɛ mbi iKrestu iYesu nani.
\v 2 Odzɛ ama abu di teyi fwo ani le gbɔ mi inɛ obwɛndɛ ibyibyi na, yilen wo ama okyɛdɔ abɔ, ama nmɛ odi otso angbeka mani.
\v 3 Shitukwu adzɛ nɛ yi eyi dafi inggisɛ oblakwutsɛ osuse mgbi iKrestu iYesu mani.
\v 4 Inggisɛ oblakwutsɛ nli kyidɔ oblakwutsɛ yɔ, li kye abɔ mgban wo ungwɔ mgbi emi ɛwɛwɛ ba, o li mina okyungwɔ no kpa ongyukwo mgban.
\v 5 Li ungwonyi yi inggisɛ nle dayayi olɛ yi angbeka, o li tu okpapyi mgbi onghaangha ba, se o ka dayayi na mi ola ngwi a wo mani.
\v 6 Inggisɛ okwɔ nkyidɔ kpɔklɔɔ yɔ, ka li inggisɛ ongwi ababɔ ogye ungwogye ongwi okwɔ nani.
\v 7 Tsɛwɛ mi odzɛ ani le gbɔ nɛni, bana Otsɛ Imgbasho ka nu abu odifwi-difwi mi ungwɔ ntonɛ duu.
\p 
\v 8 Wɛ iYesu iKrestu, o kyɛ mi etɔ mgbi iDevedi, a kyilen mi ikwu. Li Esɔ Osuse ngwi ani gbɔ,
\v 9 ngwi ani le gyadzɛ ikyon nghataa ngwi i yɛɛ ungwɔ a bwa ani adi dafi emumyi ma aani, nghaduu elodzimgbasho yɔ a bwan adi ba.
\v 10 Nghanɛ ani shitukwu alungwɔ duu mi ikye ama a sadulu ma gbɛɛ ni ama kpaa tu owatɔ-watɔ ndzɛ mbi iKrestu iYesu, yi okwɔkwɔ ogyegwu nani.
\p 
\v 11 Elodzɛ nɛ li otsitsi:
\pi1 kini eyi kwulu yan yɔ,
\q1 eyi dika dzɛ oshishe yan kpaa;
\q1 
\v 12 kini eyi shitukwu yɔ,
\q2 eyi dika kyuutɔ yan,
\q1 ni eyi tangwan yɔ,
\q2 ongwu kpaa ka tangwɛ eyi,
\q1 
\v 13 ni eyi dzɛ mi oyɛyɛ onuunu ba kpaa,
\q2 ongwu ka tila dzɛ mi oyɛyɛ onuunu,
\q1 bana o ka yama otangwɛ ewon ba.
\s1 Inggisɛ idɔ ngwu Imgbasho gbela yan
\p 
\v 14 Kiyayi owɛ ma odzɛ ntonɛni. Kwo ma adɔ mi inai Imgbasho mi ikye odzɛ oshiishi mi ayayi odzɛ, dzɛ yi abɔ oyaaya ba, li nu ama nkye adɔ ge ele dzili.
\v 15 Fya mi ofyaafya mgbi abu saan okye ewabu nu Imgbasho dafi inggisɛ ngwu Imgbasho gbela yan, dafi inggisɛ idɔ ndzɛ gyɔ o ki kwayiwi wuba di li kye abɔ byi elodzɛ otsitsi mani.
\v 16 Dulu abɔ mi onya okpaakpa mgbi ayayi odzɛ bana ama nkye ewoma tswokɛ ele ka dzɛ mbotunto yi Imgbasho saan.
\v 17 Otsootso mgbi ama ka ganya dafi ifwa nshɛ wo inggisɛ ewo mani. Dafi i dzɛ yi iHimenayɔ yi iFiletu,
\v 18 ama nboofɛ dzata otsitsi nani. A gbɔgbɛɛ okyɛɛ-kyɛɛ mi ikwu nyɛ wa, a di li ngwɔlu oyɛyɛ onuunu mgbi angbeka.
\v 19 Nghaduu itozu mgbi Imgbasho nfyumfye nɛ ka kwudzɛ kpɔklɔɔ ma, a lɔ ungwɔ to ele gbɛɛ: <<Otsɛ ye ama nli mgban, ma ali inggisɛ nkyɔ obwɛndɛ mi iyi mgbi Otsɛ tayɔ, li kyɛmɛ o ka dzata imbaali.>>
\p 
\v 20 Mi udɛ okwukwo yɔ, li okye dafi abashi bɛyi iyudza onzundzɛ ta li to ele ba, kpaa okye dafi ekwɔ yi ibɛ kpaa li to ele, angbeka li ama okye kyungwɔ imɔ mi efu, angbeka yɔ li ama okyungwɔ imɔ yan ba.
\v 21 Kini inggisɛ gbosa ewon mi odzɛɛdzɛ mgban ogbugbe yɔ, o ka li okyiidɔ imɔ, o ka yɛɛ saan, dika dzɛ yi abɔ oyaaya mbi Ongyukwo mgban, o dika wewo okyɔ ali idɔ osuse duu.
\p 
\v 22 Nghanɛ tsinya imina ibwubwe mgbi mmafa di kyɛdɔ Osaan yi oyɛyɛ onuunu yi okpitukwu bɛyi iyu yi ama nle kwu mi iyi Otsɛ yi itukwu osaan mani.
\v 23 Ka yama kyungwɔ yi ikwangha yi ayayi angwodzɛ ba, ikyena abu ye, a li ba yi odzɛ oshiishi.
\v 24 Nghaduu ongbidɔ mgbi Otsɛ yɔ, li kyɛmɛ o ka gbɔnɔgbɛ ba; kpaa o ka dzɛ wawa yi ali inggisɛ duu, o ka li inggisɛ nka yagba tsungwɔ, di dzɛ yi itukwu oshiishi yi inggisɛ ama nyumfyali.
\v 25 Ama nli gbela yan ba duu, li kyɛmɛ ngwi o ka wɛ ma odzɛ mi itukwu iyu, ikyayina Imgbasho ka nu ma kyatitukwu tso ma ofɛ kaka otsitsi,
\v 26 di nu ma yɛ luba mi odzɛɛdzɛ mgbi ama di tɔ mi ukya mgbi olodu, ongwu nteyi kwu ma ofyɛɛ tole kyɔ itukwu mgban nani.
\c 3
\s1 Ali mgbi inggisɛ mi egbe ongwi olɛlɛ
\p 
\v 1 Ye ungwɔnɛni, iTimoti, gbɛɛ mi egbe ongwi olɛlɛ ma adzɛ okwulewo ka dzɛ.
\v 2 Bana inggisɛ ka nghao di ewoma kpama itukwu bɛyi awuya mgbi ama. A kale tsaabɔ igɛgɛ, dile kyile ewo esho, le fyito, le sunu ama omba ma ba, a ka tsɛ unkonyi ba, a dika dzɛ saan ba,
\v 3 a ka dzɛ yi okpitukwu ba, a ka dzita inggisɛ yi obube ba, a kale mwonya bɛ inggisɛ, a ka bwa ewoma fyii ba, a ka di inggisɛ elela ba, ungwɔ osuse ka kpa ma ba,
\v 4 ka kye okama gya, a ka kyungwɔ mi ozoyeye ba, a ka kyile ewo esho, imina mgbi oshishe ka kpa ma ngha Imgbasho,
\v 5 a ka dzɛ dafi emi odzimgbasho mani, kpaa a ka tangwɛ mfye mgban, ungwɔ onyi no ka wo abu yi ama ba.
\p 
\v 6 A li itɔ inggisɛ ama nli dzɛ yi ofɛ le kyikyɛ mi udɛ inggisɛ kyɛ dile kpagya engyaa ama nkwu eka ba wo, ama ngwu ali ibwubwe mbwo ma itukwu, di dzɛ yi ali itɔ imina ibwubwe duu,
\v 7 a li kpayi ungwɔ alonɔ kpaa a li yagba gbela otsitsi ba.
\v 8 Dafi iJanesi yi iJambresi nose kye afɔ twɛsɛ yi iMose ma, li ngha ngwi inggisɛ ama itukwu le kplɛkplɛ di dzɛ yi oyɛyɛ onuunu otsitsi ba ntonɛ kpaa, kye afɔ twɛsɛ yi otsitsi aani.
\v 9 Nghaduu a ka kɛ mbombo yi ikwangha mgbi ama na ba, ikyekyɛ inggisɛ duu kawa difwi ikwangha mgbi ama saan saan dafi nose a difwi mgbi iJanesi bɛyi iJambresi nani.
\s1 IPol wo iTimoti ola ongwi olɛlɛ
\p 
\v 10 Mbi abu iTimoti yɔ, abu ye ali otsootso mgbi ani duu bɛyi ofɛ oshishe mgbi ani yi oweka mgbi ani yi oyɛyɛ onuunu mgbi ani yi itukwu oshiishi mgbi ani yi okpitukwu mgbi ani yi onyɔtsɛ mgbi ani okwuukwu,
\v 11 isɔ yi adzɛ itɔ ntonɛ duu kyɔ ani mi Antiɔku, iKonu bɛyi iListra, Nghaduu Otsɛ dulu ani tɔ mi ele tsatsa.
\v 12 Mi otsitsi yɔ, ama nmina odzɛ mi oshishe osunu Imgbasho mbi iKrestu iYesu yɔ, a ka gbiisɔ,
\v 13 kpaa emi ibwubwe yi ama okpagya inggisɛ wo duu ka nghao timbi-timbi, ama okpagya inggisɛ wo kpaa a dika kpagya ma wo.
\v 14 Nghaduu abu yɔ, kiyayi mi ungwɔ ngwi abu kpayi di gbela yan nani, ikyekyɛ abu ye ama ngwu abu kpayi mboma mani,
\v 15 di ye dafi wita kyɛ eyeyi ta abu ye esɔ mi Afɛ osaan, ama n yagba nu abu kwiinɛ ogbɛ owatɔ-watɔ nkyɛ ikpewo oyɛyɛ onuunu mbi iKrestu iYesu nani.
\v 16 Ali afɛ mi ibyibyilo duu kyɛ mbi Imgbasho, di dzɛ mi ikye abɔ oyaaya mi otsootso yi okyɔkyɔ odzɛ yi oyile inggisɛ dzɛ ofɛ di dzɛ ikye otso inggisɛ ofɛ odzɛ saan,
\v 17 ikye ni inggisɛ Imgbasho yile afɔ kwulɛsɛ saan okyɔ ali idɔ osuse duu mani.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 N le wo abu ola nɛ mi inai Imgbasho yi iKrestu iYesu, ongwu nkawa ba yi esutɔ mgban owa gbɔ emi oshishe yi emi ikwukwɔ ikwɔ na gbɛɛ:
\v 2 Gbeesɔ; wewo alonɔ duu; kyɔkyɔ odzɛ yi inggisɛ di kwu inggisɛ ɛwɛ wo yi itukwu oshiishi kpakpa yi odzɛ owɛɛwɛ mi ola mi ola.
\v 3 Lubana onɔ kyɛma ngwi inggisɛ ka gbela wo otsootso osuse wuba. Ikyenghanɛ, mi okyɔ imina mgbi ama a ka gbe etsetse kwuba kwutokɛ yi ama nu ma le nya ma odzɛ ngwi adɔ le gba ma gbaagba ofwo mani.
\v 4 A ka fwa otsitsi diyɛ tsɔɔshɔ okyɛdɔ ayayi utsa.
\v 5 Nghaduu abu yɔ, kwu ewabu blii mi ali ofɛ duu, shitukwu mi adzɛ ogyeegye di kyidɔ mgbi inggisɛ ogbɔ Esɔ Osuse. Di kyɔ ali idɔ ngwi Imgbasho kye wo abu abɔ duu.
\p 
\v 6 Lubana ani yɔ a teyi kye ani yangwuta dafi ungwɔ owaawa mgbi ifɛ ofɛ-fɛ mani, onɔ mgbi ani okwulu le gyɔ.
\v 7 Ani gblika osuse, ani ngyɛlu idɔ ndzɛ mi ikye ani di kwulɛsɛ mi oyɛyɛ onuunu.
\v 8 Onɛnɛ okpapyi ngwi Imgbasho kye dzɛ ama osaan dzɛ le fɛ ani fɛɛfɛ, ngwi Otsɛ, ongye ogbiikwɔ mi otsitsi, kawa kye nu ani mi egbe nani, li ani ta ba, kpaa yi ama nle fɛ oyɛɛyɛ mgban duu.
\s1 Ola mgbi iPol abuon
\p 
\v 9 ITimoti, Fya mi ofyaafya mgbi abu ba mbi ani plɛ,
\v 10 lubana iDema, ikyegbɛɛ ɛsɛ nɛ kpan itukwu nɛ, o dzita ani lu iTesalonika. IKreskɛn lu iGalatia, iTaitusu di lu iDamatia.
\v 11 I sisi iLuku ta dzɛ yi ani, kye iMaki wafɔ yi abu ba ikyesinɛ o dzɛ yi ani abɔ oyaaya mi idɔ mgbi ani.
\v 12 Ani dɔ iTacikɔ esɔ lu Efesu.
\v 13 Ni abu ka ba yɔ, kye angwuto otukwu ofu ngwi ani dzanta yi iKapu mi iTroa, yi afɛ ofulufulu, onghaangha duu ama nghao li imɔ ngwi a mɛ mi okpa ntona byi.
\p 
\v 14 Alekidzanda inggisɛ onduufa kyɔ ani ungwɔ obube kpakpa. Otsɛ iYesu ka yile mkpa kpan mi ungwɔ ngwi o kyɔ nani.
\v 15 Abu kpaa gbɛwɛbyi ewabu mi ikye mgban, ikyekyɛ o kye afɔ twɛsɛ kpɔklɔɔ yi esɔ mgbi eyi.
\p 
\v 16 Ababɔ ngwi a kye ani ba mbi ongye ogbiikwɔ ma, inggisɛ onyi kpaa kyɛ ani iyikpa ba, ali inggisɛ duu tse dzɛnta. No ka yɛɛ ungwɔ obube mi ikye ma ba.
\v 17 Nghaduukpaa Otsɛ Imgbasho fyi ani anya di nu ani mfye, ikyegbɛɛ mi ikpewo ani nu ma gbeesɔ na saan ni Udzengye duu fwon. A di dulu ani tɔ mi ondu ugaba.
\v 18 Otsɛ ka dulu ani tɔ mi ali ika ibwubwe dika kye ani kaka esutɔ mgban ongwi esho saan. Mbon okwɔkwɔ dzɛ nghataa gyegwu. No dzɛ ngha.
\s1 Angba ongwi olɛlɛ
\p 
\v 19 Ta iPrisila angba yi Akwila bɛyi etɔ mgbi Onesiforu duu.
\v 20 Erastu dzɛ iKorinti ma, ani di dzata iTrofimu ladzɛ ootse mi iMiletu.
\v 21 Fya mi ofyaafya mgbi abu ni abu ba wa kaka mmɛnɛ duuse ni owa bɛsɛ. Eyubulu yi iPudɛn yi iLainusu yi iKladia bɛyi ama onoyɛyɛ duu le ta abu angba.
\v 22 Otsɛ no dzɛ yi onodzi mgbi abu. Elela mgban no dzɛ yi ema duu.
